Creme Factory
de_cfactor

Map by MarkQ/Turd Furguson

Cremecorp is a company that supplies local twinkie factories with fresh creme filling. But as some have discovered, Cremecorp has a secret. It recovers the ubitquious filling with material from raw sewage. 
From an ingenious system devised by an expert architect, a four-step process takes the softest parts of the sewage and ferments it into fresh creme filling. Disgusted Terrorists has decided to stop this process, either midway in the processing step, or in the final step of export. Due to an anonymous tip, Cremecorp has mobilized it's 
private security force and is ready for the attack.

I've been working on this for a while, but it's my first release. 
I think it's fun to play.

ANY BUGS/SUGGESTIONS, PLEASE EMAIL ME AT: sniperx87@hotmail.com
